    public interface ClassifierFeature
extends NamedElement
    A representation of the model object 'Classifier Feature'. A classifier feature declares a behavioral or structural characteristic of instances of classifiers.

    The following features are supported:

    • Featuring Classifier

    See Also:

    • Method Detail

      • getFeaturingClassifiers

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<Classifier> getFeaturingClassifiers()
        Returns the value of the 'Featuring Classifier' reference list. The list contents are of type Classifier. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Classifier Feature'. The Classifiers that have this ClassifierFeature as a feature.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Featuring Classifier' reference list.
        See Also:
        Aadl2Package.getClassifierFeature_FeaturingClassifier(), Classifier.getClassifierFeatures()
